  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, in meantime, those guys [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] went in for the-- begging for food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And instead, to steal their-- [INAUDIBLE] I took off and went to the railroad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second time, when I come to this town, I met the-- this lady.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She told me already where the ghetto is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And she told me, there's another side from the river.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's not far from Vinnitsa, and I should go this and this direction.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went back already to the railroad to find my train to escape to Romania-- was there, Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I am by the railroad, there, and there's a lot of Germany army were loading their-- their tanks, their cannons, their wagons, their trucks, and their cargo trains.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from far away, I saw those guys, the farmermen-- they're looking for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A train moved out in the same direction, I jumped, and I went in the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And before nighttime, I reached the town, a little town, Brailov-- was before the border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There, the train stopped, because there was a checkpoint, and the Germans came over to the train and asked for the documents for everybody.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't have any documents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But was people, the other people, like they released in Germany, there's that special documents to go to the other side of the river to Romania legally.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us off of the train, and they're checking the documents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They go first-- we'll go to older people, not to you young little boys, like me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I make-believe to have-- that I go to relieve myself to close to the cargo train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I stay a minute, a minute-- I see they're reading the passports, about that, and I ran away in the field.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
